<h1>New Flickr User Claim Request</h1>

<p>
  A user has requested to claim a Flickr user account.
</p>

<h2>Details</h2>

<p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Photonia User:</strong> <%= @user.email %> (#<%= @user.serial_number %>)</li>
    <li><strong>Flickr Username:</strong> <%= @flickr_user.username %></li>
    <li><strong>Flickr NSID:</strong> <%= @flickr_user.nsid %></li>
    <li><strong>Flickr Profile:</strong> <a href="<%= @flickr_user.profileurl %>"><%= @flickr_user.profileurl %></a></li>
    <li><strong>Claim Type:</strong> Manual</li>
    <% if @reason.present? %>
    <li><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= @reason %></li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
</p>

<h2>Actions</h2>

<p>
  Click one of the links below to approve or deny this claim:
</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= @approve_url %>">Approve Claim</a> | <a href="<%= @deny_url %>">Deny Claim</a>
</p>

<p>
  Alternatively, you can manage claims in the <a href="<%= users_admin_settings_url %>">Admin Settings</a>.
</p>

<p>
  Your friendly Photonia bot.
</p>
